OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSteve Coogan and firms sued
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fover Richard III film      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Steve Coogan is being sued for libel by
OL,6, a university official who claims he was
OL,7, made to look "devious" and             
OL,8, "weasel-like" in a film about the      
OL,9, discovery of Richard III's remains.    
OL,11,FRichard Taylor has started legal action
OL,12,Fagainst the comedian, who was a writer 
OL,13,Fand producer of The Lost King.         
OL,15,FMr Taylor said he was unhappy about the
OL,16,Fway his character was portrayed.       
OL,18,FThe film told the story of the search  
OL,19,Ffor the Plantagenet monarch under a    
OL,20,FLeicester council car park in 2012.    
